title: The Data ( Use and Access ) Act | Mayer Brown
combined_text: The Data ( Use and Access ) Act | Mayer Brown. jdsupra.com.
summary: The Data Use and Access Act introduces obligations regarding data access, impacting data handling for startups. The Act mandates permitted uses like healthcare operations, requiring secure and compliant data practices. Penalties include fines up to $1,000,000 per violation, demanding data governance prioritization.

title: DOJ Final Rule on Bulk Data Transfers : A Road Map | Epstein Becker & Green
combined_text: DOJ Final Rule on Bulk Data Transfers : A Road Map | Epstein Becker & Green. jdsupra.com.
summary: The DOJ's final rule broadens data access for law enforcement, impacting data startups' compliance obligations significantly. The rule mandates providers disclose bulk data if they have knowledge of potential criminal activity, a serious concern. Data startups face increased legal risk and compliance costs, requiring them to implement robust data governance frameworks.
